  <title>Opportunity International : Empowering communties for water, sanitation &amp; clean energy</title>
  <description>The project will aim to improve the health and wellbeing of impoverished families in Bihar through a community based education programme and the provision of small loans for the installation of improved household water and sanitation infrastructure and clean energy solutions. The project will aim to deliver health and hygiene workshops and will provide loans to clients to enable the installation of toilets, water systems and biogas stoves. Opportunity have received Scottish Government funding to work in India since 2010.</description>
